{"id": "1479810989397381212", "channel_id": "1478984182725349407", "type": 19, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "说得好像也是<:Brown_think:1459080117308620996> \n感觉有点反直觉，但完全合理\n不过根据本人测试，我发现了另一个问题", "timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:00:33.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["357866427421687818"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1479525965506936895", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479813070766215200", "channel_id": "1478984182725349407", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "「静默守望」的机制除了费用+1和保留功能之外，回复生命和护盾翻倍也同样是此卡的机制，但对比图1和图2可以发现，图1是拥有「静默守望」机制，而图2没有\n两张卡都模仿了珈伦的「防御」(看图3中得到的的狂气数值可知)，理论上来说图1得到的护盾量应该是44，因为机制上吃了算力+1，所以护盾应该翻倍，但是没有", "timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:08:49.668000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:09:19.537000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479813068530782370", "filename": "IMG_20260307_193600.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 441848}, {"id": "1479813069118115873", "filename": "IMG_20260307_195840.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 429808}, {"id": "1479813069893795952", "filename": "IMG_20260307_193623.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 782354}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479813733302931649", "channel_id": "1478984182725349407", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "这里再附上一张珈伦「静默守望」的技能描述", "timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:11:27.629000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:11:33.014000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1479813733025976360", "filename": "IMG_20260307_201031.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 576428}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
