{"id": "1479821021908570263", "channel_id": "1478984182725349407", "type": 0, "author_id": "357866427421687818", "author_name": "passerbycat", "author_bot": false, "content": "我猜是\n詞綴本身是作用在卡片上\n但敘述是作用在靜默守望上\n導致你換牌後無法共享效果", "timestamp": "2026-03-07T12:40:25.368000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1479829342166192219", "channel_id": "1478984182725349407", "type": 0, "author_id": "874937440605974549", "author_name": "ka_0414", "author_bot": false, "content": "那这段描述的作用只吃一半，而且吃的是算力+1的部分也很糟糕<:Helot_slack_off:1459092159465521184> \n虽然实战中可能不容易遇到，但还是有必要再调整一下这方面的作用或描述\n要么让塔薇那些沾上算力+1的卡吃到本该有的效果，要么把这一段的描述写得再明确一些，明确写出这生命回复和护盾翻倍是只有静默守望才有作用<:Helot_slack_off:1459092159465521184>", "timestamp": "2026-03-07T13:13:29.072000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-07T13:14:19.188000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
